### Requirement Clarify Manager - REST Client
### TC-013 ~ TC-019: PATCH /api/v1/requirements/{id}/status
### 서버: http://localhost:8080 (local profile)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 0. 준비: 요구사항 생성 (TC-001 기반)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create Requirement for status test
# @name createReq
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"

{"projectName":"WorkflowTest","requirementNo":"REQ-STS-100","version":"1.0.0"}
--boundary--

### 추출된 ID 변수 설정 (IntelliJ HTTP Client 용)
@reqId = {{createReq.response.body.id}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-013 | 상태전이-정상 | Draft -> Clarifying 전이
# 기대: 200 OK, status="Clarifying"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TC-013
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Clarifying"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-014 | 상태전이-정상 | Clarifying -> Clarified 전이
# 기대: 200 OK, status="Clarified"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TC-014
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Clarified"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-015 | 상태전이-정상 | Clarified -> In Progress 전이
# 기대: 200 OK, status="In Progress"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TC-015
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "In Progress"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-016 | 상태전이-정상 | In Progress -> Done 전이
# 기대: 200 OK, status="Done"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TC-016
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Done"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-017 | 상태전이-예외 | 비정상 상태 건너뛰기 (Draft -> Done 직접 전이 시도)
# 새 요구사항 생성 후 테스트
# 기대: 400 Bad Request (또는 서버 설정에 따른 에러), ERR-STS-001
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create new req for TC-017
# @name createReq2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"

{"projectName":"WorkflowTest","requirementNo":"REQ-STS-200","version":"1.0.0"}
--boundary--

###
@reqId2 = {{createReq2.response.body.id}}

### TC-017 (Skip transition)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId2}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Done"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TC-019 | 상태전이-예외 | 완료건 수정 방어 (Done -> Draft 역전이 시도)
# 전제: TC-016에서 생성된 {{reqId}} 가 Done 상태여야 함
# 기대: 500 Internal Server Error (또는 403/400), ERR-STS-002
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TC-019 (Modify Done requirement)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/requirements/{{reqId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Draft"
}
